t></a> <span>by <a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/steve-berman/">Steve Berman</a></span></div></div><div class="article-content"><h2><a href="https://theresurgent.com/2020/04/17/trumps-opening-up-america-again-on-paper-its-great-in-practice-probably-not/">Trump&#8217;s &#8220;Opening Up America Again&#8221;: On Paper, It&#8217;s Great, In Practice, Probably Not</a></h2><div class="article-excerpt"><p>While on paper, Trump&#8217;s plan seems rational, reasonable, and well organized, in practice, it will be a collection of fits and starts, one step forward and two steps back events, new hotspots, factorie &hellip;</p></div><div class="author-meta post-meta"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/steve-berman/" class="avatar"><img alt='' src="//theresurgent.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3178b5c1fde83d61fea05115ea0a8458?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset="" data-srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3178b5c1fde83d61fea05115ea0a8458?s=192&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='lazy lazy-hidden avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' /><noscript><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3178b5c1fde83d61fea05115ea0a8458?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3178b5c1fde83d61fea05115ea0a8458?s=192&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' /></noscript></a> <span>by <a href="https://theresurgent.com/author/steve-berman/">Steve Berman</a></span></div><div class="post-meta time-meta"><time datetime="2020-04-17">2 days ago</time></div></div></div><div class="article-entry d-flex d-md-block"><div class="article-img"><a href="https://theresurgent.com/2020/04/16/stacey-abrams-and-bidens-vp-hunt/"><img width="1400" height="875" src="https://theresurgent.com/wp-content/uploads/AP_18136148498581-1400x875.jpg" class="auto-size" alt="" /></a><div class="author-meta offset-meta"><a href="https://t